<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ص ر ح<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٢٩٩٢ - ص ر ح]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>صرُحَ يَصرُح، صَراحةً وصُرُوحةً، فهو صارِح وصَريح<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• صرُح الشَّيءُ:</span> صفا وخلُص ممّا يشوبه <span class="c1">"صَرُح نسبُه/ اللَّبنُ"</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">• صرُح الأمرُ:</span> بان وأصبح واضحًا <span class="c1">"صرُح الحقُّ/ القولُ"</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>